Françoise Prévost (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fran%C3%A7oise_Pr%C3%A9vost_(actress) 0 Françoise Prévost (13 January 1930 – 30 November 1997) was a French actress, journalist and author. She was the daughter of writer Marcelle Auclair. She appeared in more than 70 films between 1949 and 1985.
